ch.nolix.element.color

Class Color

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.nolix.element.basic.Element
      • ch.nolix.element.color.Color
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IController, IControlleroid, DeterminedSIMPLE_CLASS_NAMEd, Specifiable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BackgroundColor, LinesColor, TextColor

    public class Color
extends Element
    This class represents a true color. A true color is a color that consists of a blue, green and red value that have all the size of 1 byte.
